18. GCM is an example of:
    A. Hashing
    B. AEAD
    C. Public-key exchange
    D. Digital signature

19. The main goal of AEAD is:
    A. Compression only
    B. Confidentiality plus integrity
    C. Faster password storage
    D. Key stretching

20. Governance is mainly about:
    A. Writing malware defenses only
    B. Direction, oversight, and accountability
    C. Disk imaging
    D. Packet sniffing

21. Risk treatment options include all except:
    A. Avoid
    B. Mitigate
    C. Transfer
    D. Encrypt

22. ISO/IEC 27001 is centered on:
    A. ISMS
    B. Penetration testing only
    C. Virus scanning only
